      "name": "Relative hemolysis index comparison across 5 operating points",
      "description": "CFD-predicted relative hemolysis index (RH) was compared against experimental measurements at five flow-speed combinations. All five operating points yielded RH < 1, satisfying the acceptance criterion. The comparison showed mean absolute error of 0.07 RH units across the test matrix. Results were obtained from simulation runs conducted on the FDA generic centrifugal pump geometry."
