    "rationale": "All seven assessed credibility factors achieved their required levels for MRL 2. The relative hemolysis index QoI satisfies the RH < 1 acceptance criterion across all five operating points. Six factors were not assessed, consistent with MRL 2 requirements. The overall credibility evidence is sufficient to support the COU decision that the CFD model can identify worst-case hemolysis operating conditions for the Class II CPB device.",
